    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, trim your <strong>green beans</strong>, then chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>green beans</strong> to the pan with the chicken</p>",
      "order": 4,
