    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to the pan and stir it into the sauce around the chicken, so the flour soaks up the juices, then add the <strong>creamy garlic stock</strong></p>",
