    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse your<strong> sweetcorn</strong> and<strong> butter beans</strong> and add them to the pan</p><p>Roughly tear <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>basil </strong>(save some for garnish!) into the pan and season with a generous crack of <strong>black pepper </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Mix everything together and cook covered, stirring occasionally, for 12 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your<strong> Cajun-style chicken thigh & sweetcorn casserole</strong></p>",
